Openpyxl is a Python library for reading and writing Excel (with extension xlsx/xlsm/xltx/xltm) files.
The openpyxl module allows Python program to read and modify Excel files.

For example, user might have to go through thousands of rows and pick out few handful information to make small
changes based on some criteria. Using Openpyxl module, these tasks can be done very efficiently and easily.




Use this command to install openpyxl module :


sudo pip3 install openpyxl